<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-4bede9c00223593d39b01a95ce948d30d48db773">The Cloak of Thingol [1,+18]</h2>
<em>A sable-hued cloak, with glowing elven-runes to restore magic showing calm and clear as moonlight on still water.</em> <p>
It can be activated for recharging every 70 turns if it is being worn.  It increases your dexterity and charisma by 3. It provides immunity to paralysis. It provides resistance to acid, fire and cold. It provides a random ability. 
</p>
